sentences: Hanna Borysivna Korsun (Ukrainian: Ганна Борисівна Корсун; née Popeliukh, Ukrainian: Попелюх; born 15 February 1991), known professionally as Maruv (stylized in all caps), is a Ukrainian singer, composer, poet and producer.
In 2014, she graduated in a non-musical subject from the Polytechnic Institute in Kharkiv.
